  <description><![CDATA[<p>The traditional Alpina &amp; Savoy is one of the oldest hotels in the resort and has been family-run for over 100 years. It enjoys a quiet, elevated position between Crans and Montana, only 300m from the ski lifts, and offers good facilities, including large indoor pool, as well as spectacular panoramic views. The hotel receives excellent feedback for its service and welcoming ambiance.</p>
<p><strong>'Ski Inclusive' offer is valid for bookings 13 - 19 Dec and from 3 Jan to end of season</strong> and includes: 7 nights accommodation on half board basis, 6-day whole area lift pass, 6-day ski hire, <strong>Free</strong> equipment delivery, Sfr30 bar credit per couple and <strong>Free</strong> use of ski lockers at the lift - Book by 30 November for this very special offer, exclusive to Inghams.</p>]]></description>
